    <!-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------->
    <!-- -------------------------About Me-------------------------------------->
    <!-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------->    
    <a name="aboutme"><h3>About Me</h3></a>
    <!--[<A HREF="./res/cv/chongyang_xu_cv.pdf">CV</A>]-->
    <p>I'm a Ph.D student at Max Planck Institute for Informatics (MPI-INF), working with <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/yitingxia/home">Yiting Xia</a>, starting from June 2022.</p>
    <p>I got my B.E. degree from <a href="https://www.sc.sdu.edu.cn/">School of Software</a>, <a href="https://www.sdu.edu.cn/">Shandong University</a> in 2017. 
        &nbsp;I received my M.S. degree from <a href="http://scse.buaa.edu.cn/">School of Computer Science & Engineering</a>, <a href="https://www.buaa.edu.cn/">Beihang University</a> in 2020. Until May 2022, I worked as a software engineer for Intel's Image Processing Unit 6.</p>
    <p>I'm interested in Cloud systems and Networks. I'm also interested in parallel computing and graph systems.</p>
    <br>

